title: Best Games Of The Year… So Far (Just The Bits) with Morgan: PART 2

description:
This part of the podcast I countdown the 7 best games the show has played so far this year from 7 to 1. This includes blind karaoke, easy trivia, and 5 others! You’ll be able to listen to them uninterrupted with just a few intros!
